Concerts/events application

application that finds events/concerts in the user's local area.

APIs to use: 
1)Google Maps
2)Eventbright/songkick
3)Google calendar
4)Yelp

Third Party API:
?
geolocation (built-in?)
google account
time?
yelp


Framework: 
FLEXBOX
Foundation
GRID

Basic functionality:
user can search for events their area for a given date and type of event (Genre)
User can filter results by price and rating
5 day forcast for events
distance from current location
event info (date, time, cost, band, genre)
link to buy tickets
link to venue
direction to the venue
save as favorite or watch list
share link



